body: @yaroslavvb is correct, `_pywrap_tensorflow.so` only exports symbols that have `tensorflow` in them. It is indeed strange that the `png*` symbols are leaked from`_pywrap_tensorflow.so`  even with the [linker script](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/tf_version_script.lds) only allowing `tensorflow` symbols. @llhe, do you have any ideas why this may be?
